title: Leading FMCG brands in the United Kingdom ( UK ) 2018 , by consumer reach
summary: This is a bar chart representing Food Groups in the x axis and Consumer Reach Points in millions in the y axis.
The Consumer Reach Points in millions is appeared to be the highest at Food Groups Warburtons and lowest at Food Groups Birds Eye.
The Consumer Reach Points in millions of Food Groups Birds Eye is 2.99% smaller than the maximum value at Warburtons.
